title: Gorgeous 3 Bed/2 bath rental in Southie with Parking!
map_address: 111A West 8th St Unit O near E St
posting_body: ['Available September 15th or October 1st - Southie with parking!', 'This gorgeous sundrenched South Boston rental condo has it all!', 'Three beds and two full baths, including a spacious master suite!', 'Brand new stainless steel appliances and hardwood floors (new pictures to follow).', 'An abundance of natural sunlight pours in through the oversized windows and the high ceilings give a semblance of old world character and charm.', 'Open-concept in the living/dining area and TONS of closet space.', 'Enjoy the outdoors from your private deck, accessible from two bedrooms, or cool off inside with central A/C!', 'Other conveniences include laundry in the building, a private storage unit, and most importantly for South Boston, your own DEEDED PARKING SPACE!', 'Experience all that Southie has to offer, with lots of hip restaurants and bars, easy access to public transportation and highways, and close proximity to downtown Boston.', "Contact Derek at the Galvin Group before it's too late!", 'First, last, full broker fee, and $1000 security deposit due at lease signing.', 'Sorry, no pets.']
